{"tid":2062870,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑政治原因上唔到熱門","createTime":"2020-06-13T12:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T15:40:45.000Z","uid":187489,"like":102,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"e7404e49309b8fb9f74424db2c73fccbc70df396","tid":2062870,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:42:59.000Z","msg":"推左十幾頁都上唔到熱門係咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[615黑衣白絲帶] 民陣呼籲615全港黑衣、佩戴白絲帶，悼念梁凌杰逝世一周年。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2058235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2058235</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n#15Jun #全港 #悼念梁凌杰 #全民黑衫<br />\n【梁凌杰先生逝世一年 - 6.15全城黑衣白絲帶日】<br />\n日期 : 6月15日 (一)<br />\n時間 &amp; 地點 : 任何地方<br />\n*民陣秘書署成員當晚將到太古廣場悼念<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GMBG3ni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGMBG3ni.jpg&h=7081e5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront/3125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2F3125&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrpMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=27c3a264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront/3125</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCCOJoi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCCOJoi.jpg&h=4d9b2333&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#15Jun #全港 #悼念梁凌杰 #全民黑衫<br />\n【梁凌杰先生逝世一年 - 6.15全城黑衣白絲帶日】<br />\n日期 : 6月15日 (一)<br />\n時間 &amp; 地點 : 任何地方<br />\n*民陣秘書署成員當晚將到太古廣場悼念<br />\nSource : <a href=\"https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront/3125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2F3125&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrpMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=27c3a264\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront/3125</a><br />\n<br />\n班黑警有機會介入或做大型SS，唔好以為悼念佢地就唔咬人<br />\n唔好忘記將軍澳尚十，過百人被SS，之後先放人走<br />\n<br />\nby 齊推行動做文宣巴打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">615 全港 黑衫、白絲帶<br />\n</span></span><br />\n民陣呼籲615全港黑衣、佩戴白絲帶，悼念梁凌杰逝世一周年。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2058235\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2058235</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">615民陣回歸 黑衫白絲 PP悼念    620 大型公投</div></span>"},{"pid":"6dcb139f81a950de3212e907c40ad0b9abf72d33","tid":2062870,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:44:13.000Z","msg":"樓主試下再開post<br />\n我幫手推"},{"pid":"e4ab62de90c77c9c008f20a2ad0d7c97bab4fea8","tid":2062870,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:44:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"371e59f9db5368397594e0c5367677ef36327a98","tid":2062870,"uid":87891,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:45:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"19e2b0b6e9a1e0cae052b8a201d404ffbfd7d89e","tid":2062870,"uid":50891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:45:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28751106c5dabe8e69c328644d76bf544123a67c","tid":2062870,"uid":86742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:45:39.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a142bd5267cec36fe7f2a06425666b9b8552b55","tid":2062870,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6dcb139f81a950de3212e907c40ad0b9abf72d33","tid":2062870,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:44:13.000Z","msg":"樓主試下再開post<br />\n我幫手推"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:45:58.000Z","msg":"巴打，post會有bug?<br />\n你去開啦一係 我到時pin你條link<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":